issues.description: The order of attributes specified in the problem text (lectureName, inscribed, guest, lecturers, tutors) conflicts with the order shown in the UML diagram (inscribed, lectureName, lecturers, guest, tutors), which will confuse students when implementing the constructor parameters and cause tests to fail.
issues.suggested_fix: Unify the attribute order: either update the UML diagram to list attributes as lectureName, numberOfInscribedStudents, numberOfGuestStudents, numberOfLecturers, numberOfTutors, or adjust the text to follow the UML order so the expected constructor parameter order is clear.
